{"tid":270064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波台手足又上新聞喇喂","createTime":"2017-06-04T05:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T05:52:25.000Z","uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1f16ce1c39bc3463f9a68c308b1c71ebfd9b49","tid":270064,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170604/large/1496547629_59da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170604%2Flarge%2F1496547629_59da.jpg&h=ca91783a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意甲冠軍祖雲達斯喺今屆歐聯4強對西甲勁旅巴塞隆拿，首回合大勝3:0之後，次回合雖然賽和0:0都依然順利晉級決賽。不過去到星期六嘅決賽，祖記面對西甲冠軍皇家馬德里上半場以1:1逼和對手，但下半場就再失三球而屈居亞軍。對於祖記今場輸波，有網民覺得係對巴塞首回合嘅成功搞到祖記諗得太多，有人覺得係希古恩同保羅戴巴拿呢啲球員冇表現，不過最多人講嘅就始終係祖記體力不足，尤其下半場表現同上半有好大分別。<br />\n<br />\n部分網民意見<br />\n＠做羊啊你︰BBC決賽怯場<br />\n＠芽成艮︰戴巴拿NOT FOUND<br />\n＠Raul︰成隊都垃圾架啦 連dybala都隱形<br />\n＠中七理︰認真　體力問題　50幾分鐘　一斷波回唔切氣追番<br />\n@agger路︰出3中堅先係輸波原因<br />\n@F_Torres9︰太老　體力唔夠<br />\n@6點半呻吟︰上半場蛆太出力，下半場俾皇馬屈體力<br />\n@Shawn_Marion︰冇力啦大佬 佢逼左成場你就大部分時間縮左係自己半場 個體力分野太大<br />\n@綠帽奇俠︰大半正選都三字頭，仲要擺343攻X皇馬想偷雞<br />\n@淺倉南︰dybala起碼好過希古恩啦，希古恩除咗開波個陣cup過人射左球遠射都唔記得有咩表現<br />\n@點解你要X多次︰希古恩大賽冇影 好正常<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資料來源︰<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56781383&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56781383%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170604&d=FWGQGMRI8%2BR9BXZI3QvkeTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7034f90a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56781383%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170604&h=f77cb97d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56781383&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170604</a><br />\n<br />\n連登好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ffdbd8a927b43db0f4dd8ee1e111ba52f65de9","tid":270064,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"@agger路︰出3中堅先係輸波原因<br />\n呢條辣殺上到報is a恥辱"}]}